info.author: Michael D'Agosta
info.description: A combination of tools and framework, Aegis has multiple different uses. You can import it and use the thoroughly made and tested functions. You can use it as a natural extension for the tornado web framework. And you can use it to quickly create a new web application with the structure already built-in, and follow along.
info.name: aegis-tools
info.summary: Aegis is a set of battle-tested tools and tricks to help everyone make better software
